"```sql\nSELECT COUNT(*) / 12 AS monthly_average_schools_opened\nFROM schools\nWHERE County = 'Alameda'\n  AND DOC = '52'\n  AND YEAR(OpenDate) = 1980;\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the monthly average number of schools that opened in Alameda County under the jurisdiction of the Elementary School District in 1980. It filters the schools table for records where the county is Alameda, the District Ownership Code (DOC) is 52 (indicating an Elementary School District), and the opening year is 1980. The total count of such schools is divided by 12 to get the monthly average."